column5: im heading there tomorrow morning!.. anyone else heading?
Gym tomorrow , school saturday, sunday bass pro!!
Im dieing to go down.. not till the 14th for me..  hope theres inventory left.. hahahahahaha

gotta work friday but right after i get home  from brookies and rainbows saturday ,,,,  i'm blowin' the dust off the VISA for a shop-a-thon . gonna pick up a new reel for sure .  the cold really affected 2 of my shimano's this winter , the drag seems to freeze up and  lost a couple fish 'cause of it on hook-set.[ one of which was on the saturday at the island lake derby]  she didn't engage at all . sooooo i thought i should get some insurance in a new reel while i'm figuring out  what went wrong . just gotta sell the idea now ,, like asking for myallowance again,lol.
I'll be heading up on Saturday, and Monday.
I will be there around 9:30 this morning.
I guess I could stop by.....  G
waiting for the reel trade in...is it just my imagination or is the reel trade in less of a deal this year?
By the sounds of it, by the time the reel trade in guys like me get out there, nothing's gonna be left..
Bought a couple of reels yesterday. Wasn't worth waiting for the trade in to begin. At least not for me. I would have only saved ten dollars and take a chance the ones I wanted would be sold out.
